content: This increase was due in large part to a comparable net sales increase of 10.4 million or 18.5% to 66.4 million in the third quarter of fiscal 2023, compared to 56.1 million in the prior year period related to higher point of sales transactions, driven by strong promotional campaigns and the addition of 41 new showrooms and 13 new kiosks.
